CHIN WAH KEE, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. March 3, 1928. Rehearing Denied Márch 31, 1928. No. 5063. Chandler C. Luzenberg, of New Orleans, La., for appellant. Wayne G. Borah, U. S. Atty., and E. E. Talbot, Asst. U. S. Atty., both of New Orleans, La., for the United States.

Before WALKER, BRYAN, and POSTER, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The order or decree appealed from is affirmed.
